import React from 'react';
import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';
import {
  AppBar,
  Toolbar,
  Typography,
  Button,
  Box,
  Container,
  Paper
} from '@mui/material';
import { Pets } from '@mui/icons-material';

function LandingPage() {
  const navigate = useNavigate();

  return (
    <Box sx={{ minHeight: '100vh', backgroundColor: '#f5f5f5' }}>
      {/* Navigation Bar */}
      <AppBar position="static" sx={{ backgroundColor: '#2196f3' }}>
        <Toolbar>
          <Pets sx={{ mr: 2 }} />
          <Typography variant="h6" component="div" sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
            K9 Vision
          </Typography>

          <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 2 }}>
            <Button
              color="inherit"
              onClick={() => navigate('/login')}
              sx={{
                border: '1px solid white',
                '&:hover': { backgroundColor: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.1)' }
              }}
            >
              Client Login
            </Button>
            <Button
              color="inherit"
              onClick={() => {
                // Scroll to services section
                document.getElementById('services')?.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });
              }}
            >
              Services
            </Button>
          </Box>
        </Toolbar>
      </AppBar>

      {/* Hero Section */}
      <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ mt: 8, mb: 8 }}>
        <Paper sx={{ p: 6, textAlign: 'center', backgroundColor: 'white' }}>
          <Typography variant="h2" component="h1" gutterBottom sx={{ fontWeight: 'bold', color: '#2196f3' }}>
            Welcome to K9 Vision
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="h5" color="textSecondary" paragraph>
            Professional Dog Training Client Portal
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body1" color="textSecondary" paragraph sx={{ mt: 3, mb: 4 }}>
            Stay connected with your dog's training journey. Access training videos, photos, and personalized notes from your trainer.
          </Typography>
          <Button
            variant="contained"
            size="large"
            onClick={() => navigate('/login')}
            sx={{ mt: 2, px: 4, py: 1.5 }}
          >
            Get Started
          </Button>
        </Paper>
      </Container>

      {/* Services Section */}
      <Container maxWidth="lg" id="services" sx={{ mb: 8 }}>
        <Typography variant="h3" component="h2" gutterBottom sx={{ textAlign: 'center', mb: 4, fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
          Our Services
        </Typography>
        <Box sx={{ display: 'grid', gridTemplateColumns: { xs: '1fr', md: 'repeat(3, 1fr)' }, gap: 3 }}>
          <Paper sx={{ p: 3, textAlign: 'center' }}>
            <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom color="primary">
              Client Portal Access
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
              Secure login for clients to view their dog's training progress, photos, and videos.
            </Typography>
          </Paper>
          <Paper sx={{ p: 3, textAlign: 'center' }}>
            <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom color="primary">
              Media Sharing
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
              Trainers can upload and share training videos and photos directly with clients.
            </Typography>
          </Paper>
          <Paper sx={{ p: 3, textAlign: 'center' }}>
            <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom color="primary">
              Training Notes
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary">
              Personalized notes and updates from your trainer to track your dog's progress.
            </Typography>
          </Paper>
        </Box>
      </Container>

      {/* Footer */}
      <Box sx={{ backgroundColor: '#333', color: 'white', py: 4, mt: 8 }}>
        <Container maxWidth="lg">
          <Typography variant="body2" align="center">
            Â© 2025 K9 Vision - Professional Dog Training Client Portal
          </Typography>
        </Container>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default LandingPage;
